title: ‘Better Call Saul’ S6E3
description:
Chris and Andy break down the most recent episode of ‘Better Call Saul,’ and talk about the death of a major character (1:00), how the show is already halfway through the first part of Season 6 (22:46), and what is still to come (34:33).

Hosts: Chris Ryan and Andy Greenwald
Producer: Kaya McMullen
